<node id="γ선">
  <data key="d0">γ선</data>
  <data key="d1">naturalobject</data>
  <data key="d2">γ선, also known as gamma rays, are a type of radiation categorized by their physical properties. In nuclear medicine, γ선 are utilized for the diagnosis of both physiological and pathological conditions. When measuring γ선, a Well type scintillation counter is suitable due to its excellent geometric efficiency. The appropriate energy range for γ선 is typically between 80 and 500 keV.&lt;SEP&gt;γ선 refers to gamma rays.&lt;SEP&gt;Gamma rays (γ선) are emitted from RI and detected.&lt;SEP&gt;γ선 refers to gamma rays, which are absorbed and scattered within the body, requiring correction during image reconstruction.&lt;SEP&gt;γ선에너지측정한다.&lt;SEP&gt;γ선 refers to gamma rays.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b06ed9f5e0dd9cd85ffaf0fc38757627&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-428583e70d87d887ad563511e218180d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aba8bf30078b2233792d56a3c43c08ac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5cc4f3cae46ab52d7568311ee83cce87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2a8d3df39b55d27db11892fbbfe761c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07321f301db639ed7357619e9557e638&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd28894fc7b2a8aeb26f735075d67fb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e10d247e7c97528d1ea50ec0eb927f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6259ff245a0935f93363f0b914c89df9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d099e6145645b6e4bf2bca40e46eece2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-08708d5929cf7059523d87243b280f2c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47cbfe584ecc302692a5f14daa4b7ee6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccbfd4804326f5caeaab817a2e208b7c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83b2ddf22a61c92feb5b93c9cf9b98eb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-130264f031a5f67121c20eb9f791ffb6</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1775523250</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="β선">
  <data key="d0">β선</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">β선 (beta rays) are used in nuclear medicine for diagnosing physiological and pathological conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;방사선의 한 종류로, 투과력은 α선의 약 100배이다.&lt;SEP&gt;전자를 지칭함.&lt;SEP&gt;β선 is beta ray.&lt;SEP&gt;β선 with low energy is not suitable for measurement with a Well type scintillation counter.&lt;SEP&gt;β선은 방사선의 한 종류이다.&lt;SEP&gt;β선 refers to beta rays.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b06ed9f5e0dd9cd85ffaf0fc38757627&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad2bbaf70d414921fce8a89c3f0030d8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-428583e70d87d887ad563511e218180d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aba8bf30078b2233792d56a3c43c08ac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2a8d3df39b55d27db11892fbbfe761c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd28894fc7b2a8aeb26f735075d67fb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6259ff245a0935f93363f0b914c89df9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
