  <data key="d2">Anger developed the gamma camera in 1958.&lt;SEP&gt;Anger is the person who invented the Scinticamera, gamma camera, Anger Camera in 1957 at the Donner Laboratory of California.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72590c67e60a69d417d259ef71baaf90&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73fd9633bf193d21c88e0cf35c08d9fa</data>
