<node id="Thomson Scattering">
  <data key="d0">Thomson Scattering</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Thomson Scattering, also known as 톰슨산란, involves an incident wave colliding with an atom, causing the orbital electrons to oscillate at the same frequency and emit electromagnetic waves of the same energy.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-16be9377fc737f76ca60084b1220e8de</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1775522937</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
