<node id="Gamma-Ray Emission">
  <data key="d0">Gamma-Ray Emission</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Gamma-Ray Emission is a process, and the Internal Conversion Probability is smaller than Gamma-Ray Emission.</data>
