<node id="방사성의약품">
  <data key="d0">방사성의약품</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">방사성의약품 refers to radiopharmaceuticals, which are used both for in-vivo (within the body) and in-vitro (outside the body) examinations. They are prepared for administration to patients. 방사성의약품's radioactivity can be quickly and accurately measured, such as when measuring the radioactivity within a vial. They are also utilized in medical imaging procedures.&lt;SEP&gt;방사성의약품 refers to radiopharmaceuticals used in SPECT and PET.&lt;SEP&gt;방사성의약품 are radioactive drugs that emit single photons (γ-rays) within the body.&lt;SEP&gt;방사성의약품은 생리학적, 생화학적 작용에 의해 각 장기 조직에 집적되는 물질이다.&lt;SEP&gt;방사성의약품 are radiopharmaceuticals administered to the subject for measurement after removing the calibration source.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-428583e70d87d887ad563511e218180d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07321f301db639ed7357619e9557e638&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fda9da9d7fcaa192c940b687cf738dd0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e10d247e7c97528d1ea50ec0eb927f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfe1a1928a0c8fd37b6094e61031eb3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d099e6145645b6e4bf2bca40e46eece2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d69adcec116d52c682eb46b43c5af2f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73fd9633bf193d21c88e0cf35c08d9fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a1e99e5d45d87bc110fb72539f81b91d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83b2ddf22a61c92feb5b93c9cf9b98eb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-130264f031a5f67121c20eb9f791ffb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0782c64fcf3afb545cd9c3f803922e58</data>
