</node>
<node id="3H">
  <data key="d0">3H</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">3H is used in liquid scintillation counting.&lt;SEP&gt;3H is a radioactive isotope used to label steroid hormones, emitting low-energy β-rays (18 KeV).&lt;SEP&gt;3H is an isotope used in 체외진단용방사성의약품.&lt;SEP&gt;3H has a half-life of 12.3 years and emits beta radiation of 0.0186, used for labeling organic compounds and measuring body water.&lt;SEP&gt;3H 핵종은 액체섬광을 통해 측정할 수 있다.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d83407b553bdad56b98cf8fd5be64bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-06409f405ed68573d707ceaadba57801&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-924d4e084e2a6643308b6bc76af06895&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01aeb670194fbaa7323582a61264ce3a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-78dbaba6777799b28327851a2d931cc2</data>
