<node id="Renogram Test">
  <data key="d0">Renogram Test</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">A diagnostic test that may involve rare side effects from specific radiopharmaceuticals.&lt;SEP&gt;Renogram test uses 99mTc-GH to examine kidney function, but can cause vasovagal and allergic reactions.</data>
