</node>
<node id="산란선">
  <data key="d0">산란선</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">광전효과에서 산란선은 발생하지 않는다.&lt;SEP&gt;primary photon(1차광자)을산란선이나배후방사선으로부터선별.&lt;SEP&gt;Scattered radiation that is removed to improve image quality.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-753835320b6c915866df2a673bba93bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccbfd4804326f5caeaab817a2e208b7c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04bcfb8da445fd49f5c837b6179c61bb</data>
