  <data key="d0">Point Source</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">A condition where the focal point is very small.&lt;SEP&gt;Point source is used at a distance of 1-2m to record images for Intrinsic Flood Uniformity.&lt;SEP&gt;Point Source can be used with Four-quadrant bar phantom to perform LSF and PSF tests.</data>
