<node id="123I">
  <data key="d0">123I</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">An isotope used for in-vivo labeling.&lt;SEP&gt;123I emits pure gamma rays (159 KeV), has a half-life of 13.3 hours, and is manufactured in a cyclotron.&lt;SEP&gt;123I is a radioactive isotope.&lt;SEP&gt;123I는 아이오딘의 방사성 동위원소이다.&lt;SEP&gt;An isotope with a specific energy level.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1361a0035ac4f0205b268905baaa03f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2a8d3df39b55d27db11892fbbfe761c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd28894fc7b2a8aeb26f735075d67fb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73fd9633bf193d21c88e0cf35c08d9fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6275b489d31d3ddb70252ffd8be243b7</data>
