  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">경합반응 involves adding a substance labeled with a radioactive nuclide to a reaction system where a substance and a binder that specifically binds to it react, causing a competitive reaction, and measuring the rate at which this radioactive nuclide binds to measure the amount of an unknown substance.</data>
