<node id="광전자증배관">
  <data key="d0">광전자증배관</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">광전자증배관의 광전음극(photocathode)은 섬광체에서 방출된 형광의 파장 특성과 일치해야 한다.&lt;SEP&gt;광전자증배관 refers to photomultiplier tube.&lt;SEP&gt;광전자증배관 is a photomultiplier tube attached to the rear of the scintillator.&lt;SEP&gt;광전자증배관(Photomultiplier Tube, PMT) converts visible light into photoelectrons and amplifies the signal.&lt;SEP&gt;광전자증배관은 PET 스캐너 검출 시스템의 일부이다.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6259ff245a0935f93363f0b914c89df9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d099e6145645b6e4bf2bca40e46eece2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d69adcec116d52c682eb46b43c5af2f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a1e99e5d45d87bc110fb72539f81b91d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-130264f031a5f67121c20eb9f791ffb6</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
