<node id="파고분석기">
  <data key="d0">파고분석기</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">파고분석기 refers to pulse height analyzer.&lt;SEP&gt;파고분석기 (Pulse Height Analyzer : PHA) is a component of the Rectilinear Scanner system.&lt;SEP&gt;설정된에너지범위내에있는pulse만출력한다.&lt;SEP&gt;파고분석기 (PHA, Pulse Height Analyzer) is a device used to analyze the amplitude of pulses, especially in the context of radiation detection.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6259ff245a0935f93363f0b914c89df9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc0ff97fcbf2499d0f352a78d92492f1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccbfd4804326f5caeaab817a2e208b7c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83b2ddf22a61c92feb5b93c9cf9b98eb</data>
