<node id="Image">
  <data key="d0">Image</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The image size is the same as the actual object's size.&lt;SEP&gt;Image is obtained by irradiating the phantom.&lt;SEP&gt;Image is obtained by investigating a point source in the inherent image distortion test.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-08708d5929cf7059523d87243b280f2c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-475783fc231bbcff930d8d8bc16de315&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-435f46f7df27683a6f082e9ae451704b</data>
