<node id="PHA">
  <data key="d0">PHA</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">PHA (=Spectrometer) is a device necessary for improving the image quality of a scintigram by removing scattered rays. It consists of proportional amplification and PHA.&lt;SEP&gt;A pulse-height analyzer.&lt;SEP&gt;Pulse의gain을증가시켜PHA로보낸다.</data>
