  <data key="d1">naturalobject</data>
  <data key="d2">A thallium-activated sodium iodide crystal with a density of 3.67 g/cm3, an effective atomic number of 53, and a scintillation decay time of 0.25µsec. It transforms X and gamma rays into visible light.&lt;SEP&gt;Nal(Tl) crystal is a thallium-activated sodium iodide crystal used as a scintillator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6275b489d31d3ddb70252ffd8be243b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03574e2708590c1fbd812aab77b1c581</data>
