  <data key="d0">분해능</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">분해능 refers to the resolution which varies depending on the device model, data collection method, and image reconstruction method.&lt;SEP&gt;분해능 (Resolution) is a quality control item.</data>
