<node id="Artifact">
  <data key="d0">Artifact</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Artifact refers to the occurrence of false images due to incomplete device adjustments or corrections.&lt;SEP&gt;Artifact affects image quality in SPECT due to 장치의조정이나보정.&lt;SEP&gt;영상 재구성 시 균일성과 관련된 인공 음영.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47cbfe584ecc302692a5f14daa4b7ee6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a1e99e5d45d87bc110fb72539f81b91d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b90292f9431fa43f118e063f626e7413</data>
