  <data key="d0">Collimator Resolution (Rc)</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Collimator Resolution (Rc) is the resolution of the collimator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7388f7ee8e7e66b19833edd200caba00</data>
