</node>
<node id="Intrinsic Resolution">
  <data key="d0">Intrinsic Resolution</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Intrinsic Resolution is the inherent resolution of the scinticamera itself.&lt;SEP&gt;Intrinsic Resolution is one aspect of the spatial resolution of a scinticamera.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7388f7ee8e7e66b19833edd200caba00&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-435f46f7df27683a6f082e9ae451704b</data>
