<node id="Energy Resolution">
  <data key="d0">Energy Resolution</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Energy Resolution is expressed as the FWHM of the photopeak.&lt;SEP&gt;Energy Resolution assesses the ability to distinguish gamma rays by energy, indicated by 반치폭.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7388f7ee8e7e66b19833edd200caba00&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-435f46f7df27683a6f082e9ae451704b</data>
