  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Phantom is used for quality control, specifically for spatial resolution, distortion, and linearity.&lt;SEP&gt;Phantom is a tool used to assess camera resolution when the camera's resolution differs.&lt;SEP&gt;Phantom is used for evaluating image resolution in slice phantom images.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bd9b2058fcee8557f56b570183925ebd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-34f62ef495ef155167a515f56fca8173&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-833544a0af4106771fa805c95df67753</data>
