  <data key="d0">UFOV</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">UFOV (Useful Field of View) refers to the detector's actual size, constituting 95% of the total.&lt;SEP&gt;UFOV (유효시야) is the effective field of view, outside of which the scinticamera is shielded with a lead plate.</data>
