  <data key="d0">PLES(Parallel -Line Equal Space) Phantom</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">PLES phantom은 장기 phantom의 한 종류로, 공간 분해능을 평가하는 데 사용된다.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-475783fc231bbcff930d8d8bc16de315</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1775523380</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Four Quadrant Bar Phantom">
  <data key="d0">Four Quadrant Bar Phantom</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Four Quadrant Bar Phantom is a specific type of phantom.&lt;SEP&gt;Four Quadrant Bar Phantom (사등분막대팬텀) is used in analog imaging to measure system resolution, typically performed monthly.&lt;SEP&gt;Four quadrant bar phantom은 장기 phantom의 한 종류로, 균일도를 평가하는 데 사용된다.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-475783fc231bbcff930d8d8bc16de315&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-435f46f7df27683a6f082e9ae451704b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-833544a0af4106771fa805c95df67753</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1775523380</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Smith Orthogonal Hole Phantom">
  <data key="d0">Smith Orthogonal Hole Phantom</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Smith Orthogonal Hole Phantom is a specific type of phantom.&lt;SEP&gt;Smith orthogonal hole phantom은 장기 phantom의 한 종류로, 직선성을 평가하는 데 사용된다.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-475783fc231bbcff930d8d8bc16de315&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-833544a0af4106771fa805c95df67753</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1775523380</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
