  <data key="d0">Extrinsic Resolution</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Extrinsic Resolution, specifically collimator 분해능, is another aspect of a scinticamera's spatial resolution.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-435f46f7df27683a6f082e9ae451704b</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1775523380</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
